Description: a IN ... – The in(a, b) function.

Title: a GLOBAL IN ...
Description: a GLOBAL IN ... – The globalIn(a, b) function.

Title: a GLOBAL NOT IN ...
Description: a GLOBAL NOT IN ... – The globalNotIn(a, b) function.

Title: a = ANY (subquery)
Description: a = ANY (subquery) – The in(a, subquery) function.

Title: a != ANY (subquery)
Description: a != ANY (subquery) – The same as a NOT IN (SELECT singleValueOrNull(*) FROM subquery).

Title: a = ALL (subquery)
Description: a = ALL (subquery) – The same as a IN (SELECT singleValueOrNull(*) FROM subquery).

Title: a != ALL (subquery)
Description: a != ALL (subquery) – The notIn(a, subquery) function.
